Package: chromswitch
Title: An R package for detecting chromatin state switches
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: person("Selin", "Jessa", email = "selinjessa@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An R implementation of a flexible method to detect chromatin state
    switches between samples in two biological conditions in a specific genomic
    region of interest given ChIP-seq data.
Depends: R (>= 3.3.1)
Imports:
    GenomicRanges (>= 1.26.4),
    methods
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Suggests: testthat
biocViews: MultipleComparison, Transcription, GeneExpression,
    DifferentialPeakCalling, HistoneModification, Epigenetics,
    FunctionalGenomics
